Animatronic Abilities.Darkness works in favor of the animatron: Darkness works in favor of the animatronic. Reduces the range of the glow by 10%/20%/30%, making it easier to creep up on unsuspecting survivors.
Animatronic Abilities.Fresh wounds leave a path to follow. Aft: Fresh wounds leave a path to follow. After striking a survivor, their footprints become visible for 1/2/3 seconds, making it easier to track them down.
Animatronic Abilities.A rescue won't go unheard. The animatron: A rescue won't go unheard. The animatronic is alerted when a survivor has been rescued for a ball pit, temporarily highlighting its location for 1/2/3 seconds.
Animatronic Abilities.Nothing stands in the way. Opens doors 1: Nothing stands in the way. Opens doors 10%/20%/30% faster, reducing obstacles between the animatronic and its prey.
Animatronic Abilities.Silence sharpens the senses. While stand: Silence sharpens the senses. While standing still, activates ability to detect survivors hacking nearby. A distinct sound or notification alerts both the animatronic and survivors if detected. Lasts 1/2/3 seconds.
Animatronic Abilities.The hunt isn't over yet. When the exit d: The hunt isn't over yet. When the exit doors are unlocked, the animatronic's speed increases by 7.5%/15%/20%, making last-minute escapes even more dangerous.
Animatronic Abilities.Strikes leave a lasting mark. When a sur: Strikes leave a lasting mark. When a survivor is hit, nearby teammates will be revealed with a red outline for a short duration.
Animatronic Abilities.Can throw a cupcake at the nearby surviv: Can throw a cupcake at the nearby survivor to deal damage and weaken their escape.
Animatronic Abilities.Strums a chilling chord, sending shockwa: Strums a chilling chord, sending shockwaves that slow down nearby survivors in the animatronic's presence.
Animatronic Abilities.The hooked metal hand can temporarily sa: The hooked metal hand can temporarily sabotage terminals by striking them, stalling survivors and slowing their progress.
Animatronic Abilities.Instantly knocks survivors with a powerf: Instantly knocks survivors with a powerful attack. Passive cooldown 45 seconds.
Animatronic Abilities.Can grab the nearest survivor within 50: Can grab the nearest survivor within 50 studs (Dodgeable). 30 seconds cooldown.
Animatronic Abilities.Silences footsteps and camera shake infl: Silences footsteps and camera shake influence for 5/9/13 seconds, making attacks more surprising. 30 seconds cooldown.
Animatronic Abilities.Resets the progress of the nearest termi: Resets the progress of the nearest terminal. 90 seconds cooldown.
Animatronic Abilities.When a survivor is downed, anyone within: When a survivor is downed, anyone within 35 studs of the downed survivor is instantly struck with residual damage.
Animatronic Abilities.Can create a blazing wall of fire anywhe: Can create a blazing wall of fire anywhere, forming a temporary barrier of heat that punishes anyone who dares to cross it.
Animatronic Abilities.A little companion plushie that can be p: A little companion plushie that can be placed anywhere, once placed, it grants the ability to teleport back to the plushie.
Animatronic Abilities.Drops an ice cream cone that detects nea: Drops an ice cream cone that detects nearby survivors. Can be removed by survivors.
Animatronic Abilities.Twirls around during sprints, dealing lo: Twirls around during sprints, dealing low damage (20) around itself with each spin, but the spring has a 300% longer cooldown.
Animatronic Abilities.Hitting a survivor will cause them to lo: Hitting a survivor will cause them to lose a limb that will either reduce movement speed or hacking speed. Survivors can retrieve their limbs.
Animatronic Abilities.Attacking a survivor will poison every n: Attacking a survivor will poison every nearby survivors for 10 damage every seconds for 5 seconds. 30 seconds cooldown.
Animatronic Abilities.Animatronic can drop a trap that trips s: Animatronic can drop a trap that trips survivors.
Animatronic Abilities.Some terminals are trapped. Hacking a tr: Some terminals are trapped. Hacking a trapped terminal grants the animatronic a speed boost and cooldown reduction.
Animatronic Abilities.Transfers into the digital reality by be: Transfers into the digital reality by becoming invisible for a while. When turning visible, cannot move and attack for a split second. 35 seconds cooldown.
